Libatkan target.

45:37.125 --> 45:38.041
Salin itu.

45:38.125 --> 45:39.041
Tembakkan api.

45:39.125 --> 45:40.208
Kalian orang bodoh!

45:40.291 --> 45:41.916
[roket meletus]

